{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3e08388cd","title":"在中央工作会议陈伯达发言时的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56853dd817","index":0,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"a3e08388cd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"李雪峰","id":"d699b1a5e7","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fff423f95b","type":"title","text":"在中央工作会议陈伯达发言时的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62368122f1","type":"paragraph","text":"在中央工作会议陈伯达发言时的插话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89deae83c6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eba8ba4dcc","type":"paragraph","text":"1964.12.27","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8535fdb74","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：主要矛盾是什么？主席根据大家的意见作了总结。主要矛盾是社会主义和资本主义的矛盾。四清与四不清不能说明问题的性质。封建社会就是清官与贪官的问题。《四进士》就是反贪官的嘛！","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ecad4cb97","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：巡抚出朝，地动山摇，可了不起哩！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"348d900f07","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：封建时代的清官实质上是假的。“三年清知府，十万雪花银。”清，在不同社会有不同的阶级内容。资本主义社会也有所谓清官，那些清官都是大财阀。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15be28d6f2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：清朝刘锷的《老残游记》中说，清官害人，比贪官害人还厉害。后来一查，南北朝史中的《魏史》就有此说。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2bcf37bc28","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：内部矛盾哪个时代没有？党内外矛盾交叉，党内有党。国民党也有此问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8e9a1d10b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我们党内至少有两派，一个是社会主义派，一个是资本主义派。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c129cd105","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：主席强调，要听各方面的话。好话，坏话，特别是反对的话，要耐心听。这是工作做得好坏的准则。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"acb277c73d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：讲话长了怎么办？李雪峰同志说的话，讲长了打零分。讲长了，让他讲长嘛！横直没人听嘛！","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c21a51d21e","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：许多人忘记自己是从那里来的。不能忘本嘛！我这个人不参加革命，顶多是个小学教员、中学教员而已。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89d97a20e5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：大官是从小官来的，小官是从老百姓来的。我们都是从老百姓中来的，还是老百姓嘛！“蒋委员长”不姓蒋，姓郑，叫郑三发子，河南人氏，只知有母，不知有父，还不是老百姓变的？","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40dfd77464","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：主席常说，不要自以为是。乡干部当权，就以为自己的意见对。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a94165b480","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不要当了权，就是自己的意见对。自以为是，没有自以为不是的。为什么要开会？就是意见不一致。一致了开会干什么？","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15ed4dd01d","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：不怕官，只怕管嘛！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"783b8a7d7f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：小官怕大官，大官怕洋人。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3e08388cd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}